OL,5,EMY LITTLE MISS STICKY      W"/~/!   
OL,6,E                          WW "m|?!    
OL,7, Dear Nick,                             
OL,8, BMy girlfriend's so attached to me I   
OL,9, Bmight as well be wearing a sellotape  
OL,10, Bsuit! She wants to be with me every   
OL,11,B minute of the day. I feel suffocated. 
OL,13, BWhile I love her to bits, I'd like her
OL,14, Bto back off a bit.                    
OL,16,B How do you tell a girl you'd like to  
OL,17, Bsee less of them without them thinking
OL,18, Byou want to dump them?                
OL,19,BGBrian, 16,GDudley                     
