OL,5,EMY LITTLE MISS STICKY      W"/~/!   
OL,6,E                          WW "m|?!    
OL,7, Nick replies,                          
OL,8, BEven if you really love someone you   
OL,9, Bdon't need to be with them every hour 
OL,10, Bof the day!                           
OL,12, BIt could destroy the good things you  
OL,13, Bdo have. Gently try to explain to     
OL,14, Byour girlfriend that you need to have 
OL,15, Bspace but still want to see her.      
OL,17, BIt's better to deal with this before  
OL,18, Bit gets to breaking point. Be honest  
OL,19, Band share your concerns.              
