OL,5,EMY LITTLE MISS STICKY      W"/~/!   
OL,6,E                          WW "m|?!    
OL,7, Nick replies,                          
OL,8, BIf you feel you need to see less of   
OL,9, Byour girlfriend, don't make it into a 
OL,10, Bbad thing.                            
OL,12, BLet her know how much you love her,   
OL,13, Bbut explain you need room to lead your
OL,14, Bown life too. Encourage her to see    
OL,15, Bmore of her friends.                  
OL,16,B                                       
OL,17, BRelationships that deny friendships   
OL,18, Bcan get too intense. It's healthier   
OL,19,B for both of you to be balanced.       
