OL,5,EGRUMBLE IN THE JUNGLE      W"/~/!   
OL,6,E                          WW "m|?!    
OL,7, Dear Nick,                             
OL,8, BI've met this girl who's really into  
OL,9, Bdrum n' bass. She virtually lives for 
OL,10, Bthe music and clubs every weekend.    
OL,12, BLast week I went clubbing, hoping to  
OL,13,B get to know her better, but I blew it.
OL,15, BI've never danced to drum n' bass     
OL,16,B before and couldn't get into such a   
OL,17, Bfast groove! I looked a right berk,   
OL,18, Band I'm sure she was ashamed of me.   
OL,19,BGAn ambient fan                        
