OL,5,EGRUMBLE IN THE JUNGLE      W"/~/!   
OL,6,E                          WW "m|?!    
OL,7, Nick replies,                          
OL,8, BDancing is a weird thing. It always   
OL,9, Bfeels much harder than it looks. Just 
OL,10, Bbecause you think you made a fool of  
OL,11, Byourself dancing to drum n' bass      
OL,12, Bdoesn't mean this girl did.           
OL,14, BInstead of worrying about dancing,    
OL,15, Bworry about about how you communicated
OL,17, BShe's not going to like you just      
OL,18, Bbecause you can dance. If the way you 
OL,19, Bmove matters then she doesn't care.   
