OL,5,EGRUMBLE IN THE JUNGLE      W"/~/!   
OL,6,E                          WW "m|?!    
OL,7, Nick replies,                          
OL,8, BFeeling this girl might not like you  
OL,9, Bbecause you think you can't dance to  
OL,10, Bdrum n' bass is just evidence of your 
OL,11, Binsecurity about her.                 
OL,13, BThe only way to feel more at ease with
OL,14, Bher is to spend more time talking, not
OL,15, Bdancing.                              
OL,17, BClubs are very hard places to get to  
OL,18, Bknow girls. They may be OK for meeting
OL,19, Bbut you then need time alone together.
